      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p><sub><img style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\" src=\"systems/sfrpg/images/cup/gameplay/photon.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></sub><span>&nbsp;</span>Photon Revelation</p>\n<p>Your shimmering power draws your enemies’ focus to the real threat: you. As a move action, you can focus your attention on a creature within 30 feet of you. The target must attempt a Fortitude save. If it fails, it takes a –2 penalty to attack rolls for attacks that don’t include you as a target for 1 round or until you leave photon mode.</p>"
